data_processing_submit_job_description:
OVH Analytics Data Compute lets you run Spark job on-demand with a customizable amount of vCPU cores and RAM.
Upload your code as JAR or Python files to a Swift Container, and run it using the interface below.
During your job execution you will get access to live logs and metrics.
data_processing_submit_job_spark_descrip: Submit a JAR package containing all the classes and dependencies needed by your job.
data_processing_submit_job_pyspark_descr: Submit a Python working directory with a Conda requirements file.
